<title>HIDE-ALL-NETWORKS</title>
</head>
<body>
<h3><i>This makes my semantic network invisible.</i></h3>
<h3><font size="2" color="gray">Begin micro-behaviour</font>
</h3>
<p><b>HIDE-ALL-NETWORKS</b></p>
<p><font size="2" color="gray">Begin NetLogo code:</font> </p>
<pre>ask objects with [kind = &quot;Belief Node&quot; or kind = &quot;Anchor Point&quot;]
    [set my-visibility false
     set hidden? true]
ask links
    [set hidden? true]
ask objects with [kind = "Person"] [set my-network-visibility false]</pre>
<font size="2" color="gray">End NetLogo code</font> 
<h2>Related Micro-behaviours</h2>
<p><a href="SHOW-MY-NETWORK.html">SHOW-MY-NETWORK</a> displays my network.
<a href="HIDE-MY-NETWORK.html">HIDE-MY-NETWORK</a> hides it.
<a href="TOGGLE-VISIBILITY-OF-NETWORK.html">TOGGLE-VISIBILITY-OF-NETWORK</a> 
switches its visibility. </p>
